 integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSelectComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SelectComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"select"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Select"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThe